DATA LICENSING NOTICE

This repository contains software code (licensed under MIT as above) and may
process or include data from external sources. The licensing of data differs
from the software license:

1. SOFTWARE CODE: All Python scripts, analysis tools, visualization code, and
   documentation in this repository are licensed under the MIT License above.

2. GRAVITATIONAL WAVE DATA: Data from the Gravitational Wave Open Science 
   Center (GWOSC) is used under the LIGO Open Science Center Data Release 
   Policy. See https://gwosc.org/data/ for terms and conditions.
   
3. LLAMA 4 MODELS: If using the optional Llama 4 integration, users must
   comply with Meta's Llama 4 Community License Agreement. The software code
   for integration is MIT-licensed, but the model weights are subject to
   Meta's terms. See https://ai.meta.com/llama/license/

4. SCIENTIFIC RESULTS: Analysis results, figures, and derived data products
   generated by this software should cite both this software (see CITATION.cff)
   and the original data sources (GWOSC, etc.).

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with all applicable data licenses
when using this software to process or analyze data from external sources.
